dc_description_s: This data represents Child Care Providers, for Wisconsin in 2025. [This dataset contains locations and attributes of Child Care Providers, licensed by the state of Wisconsin. The data is used for planning, management and analysis by Wisconsin Department of Health Services staff and by other government agencies.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/wi-dhs::wisconsin-trauma-centers/about
